## Git LFS for Large Images

**This repository uses Git LFS for all image files.**

- All `.webp`, `.png`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg` files are automatically tracked by Git LFS
- No manual steps needed - just commit images normally
- Prevents repository size issues and push failures
- See `docs/technical/GIT-LFS-SETUP.md` for full details

**Important:**
- Git LFS must be installed: `git lfs install`
- Images are automatically handled - no special commands needed
- If push fails with "file too large", check Git LFS is installed

